{"tid":1130942,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"有無人好鍾意王靖雯 (シャーリー・ウォン)","createTime":"2019-04-29T11:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T01:17:06.000Z","uid":92377,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fbf3cee5bdb11caf655501f750a875d898412702","tid":1130942,"uid":92377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:06:14.000Z","msg":"一個八九十年代嘅香港神級歌手 <br />\n王靖雯 (シャーリー・ウォン) Shirley Wong!!<br />\n掀起新式廣東歌熱潮<br />\n出過無數隻經典粵語歌同唱片<br />\n94年仲開左誇年聖誕演唱會<br />\n(個時得3歲遺憾只可以拎返我表姐D碟嚟睇)<br />\n佢仲拎過好多次最受歡迎女歌手獎<br />\n想知有無同好<br />\n有無人知佢去左邊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K8Lpif8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK8Lpif8.jpg&h=99ad7158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ct.yimg.com/xd/api/res/1.2/QMBi12eUzZIV766jHovgNA--/YXBwaWQ9eXR3YXVjdGlvbnNlcnZpY2U7aD01NDk7cT04NTtyb3RhdGU9YXV0bzt3PTU3Mw--/https://s.yimg.com/ob/image/0b9012da-c97c-454e-8bdd-dbfb2fec0f9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fct.yimg.com%2Fxd%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FQMBi12eUzZIV766jHovgNA--%2FYXBwaWQ9eXR3YXVjdGlvbnNlcnZpY2U7aD01NDk7cT04NTtyb3RhdGU9YXV0bzt3PTU3Mw--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fob%2Fimage%2F0b9012da-c97c-454e-8bdd-dbfb2fec0f9e.jpg&h=b703afd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mFP6UpV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmFP6UpV.jpg&h=b382aa17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z0ZnsKW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ0ZnsKW.jpg&h=6d4f1e3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eG6EuYg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeG6EuYg.jpg&h=d58af475&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gRt0epW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgRt0epW.jpg&h=42d014a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a73199c0d8bb3646accf8d7e451189526fa6a4e","tid":1130942,"uid":106326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:12:46.000Z","msg":"？？？？？"},{"pid":"2df8e42272b25c6f40ac7498eb80bbe72365459b","tid":1130942,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:13:38.000Z","msg":"我鐘意王菲多d, 王靖雯乜水黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#曲到圓"},{"pid":"5f5f333238c57fe928e541193df1f3ffd30dd679","tid":1130942,"uid":125903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:14:05.000Z","msg":"人靚聲甜<br />\n屈機到爆"},{"pid":"83384118383d48948623dad8b94509149d732f3c","tid":1130942,"uid":65887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:27:19.000Z","msg":"愛王靖雯的「貼地」<br />\n<br />\n很多人記得，王菲未叫王菲之前，是用王靖雯這個名字闖樂壇的，而其實王菲才是真名，王靖雯只是藝名。但你又記得王菲叫做Faye之前，是叫甚麼英文名字呢？答案是Shirley。<br />\n<br />\n  Shirley Wong時期其實不乏好歌，那歌路、唱腔、風格，甚至那份「貼地」感，都是王菲「一個時期的經典」，咬字不正有咬字不正的動聽，首張個人大碟《王靖雯》走抒情路 ，第一主打歌《無奈那天》是首平易近人的Ballad，成功為她打響頭炮。<br />\n<br />\n  全張碟個人最愛是《尾班車》，改編自濱田省吾的作品，由陳少琪填上廣東歌詞（陳潔靈都改編過，歌名叫《又記起你》），旋律靚，詞動人。其實自從王菲叫做王菲後，她很少會唱王靖雯的歌，但如果她肯唱，以一把成熟歌聲演繹初出道作品，感覺是另一種動聽！二○○四年十一月在紅館舉行的《菲比尋常Live！》演唱會上，「王」恩浩蕩，王菲選唱了兩首王靖雯的歌曲──《尾班車》和《靜夜的單簧管》！可以用超級好聽來形容，但好可能這並非她的個人意願，所以兩首歌都只唱了一半，實在很「吊癮」！<br />\n<br />\n  此碟內還有一首歌叫《愛聽謊言》，特別在它正是名曲《恰似你的溫柔》廣東版，潘安邦、蔡琴、鄧麗君都唱過。當年王靖雯改編，未知是她的意願，還是唱片公司主意？<br />\n<br />\n文：劉存孝<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/life/arts/20170519/141153/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Farts%2F20170519%2F141153%2F&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9Rdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=03f97324\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Farts%2F20170519%2F141153%2F&h=f18d762e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/life/arts/20170519/141153/</a>"},{"pid":"c5ce4eef430a7dafa69452132554b43ae84312ee","tid":1130942,"uid":36568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T12:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16bdb7d8c807f29aff2aed0938ef9ede2fe98cc3","tid":1130942,"uid":92377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83384118383d48948623dad8b94509149d732f3c","tid":1130942,"uid":65887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:27:19.000Z","msg":"愛王靖雯的「貼地」<br />\n<br />\n很多人記得，王菲未叫王菲之前，是用王靖雯這個名字闖樂壇的，而其實王菲才是真名，王靖雯只是藝名。但你又記得王菲叫做Faye之前，是叫甚麼英文名字呢？答案是Shirley。<br />\n<br />\n  Shirley Wong時期其實不乏好歌，那歌路、唱腔、風格，甚至那份「貼地」感，都是王菲「一個時期的經典」，咬字不正有咬字不正的動聽，首張個人大碟《王靖雯》走抒情路 ，第一主打歌《無奈那天》是首平易近人的Ballad，成功為她打響頭炮。<br />\n<br />\n  全張碟個人最愛是《尾班車》，改編自濱田省吾的作品，由陳少琪填上廣東歌詞（陳潔靈都改編過，歌名叫《又記起你》），旋律靚，詞動人。其實自從王菲叫做王菲後，她很少會唱王靖雯的歌，但如果她肯唱，以一把成熟歌聲演繹初出道作品，感覺是另一種動聽！二○○四年十一月在紅館舉行的《菲比尋常Live！》演唱會上，「王」恩浩蕩，王菲選唱了兩首王靖雯的歌曲──《尾班車》和《靜夜的單簧管》！可以用超級好聽來形容，但好可能這並非她的個人意願，所以兩首歌都只唱了一半，實在很「吊癮」！<br />\n<br />\n  此碟內還有一首歌叫《愛聽謊言》，特別在它正是名曲《恰似你的溫柔》廣東版，潘安邦、蔡琴、鄧麗君都唱過。當年王靖雯改編，未知是她的意願，還是唱片公司主意？<br />\n<br />\n文：劉存孝<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/life/arts/20170519/141153/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Farts%2F20170519%2F141153%2F&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9Rdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=03f97324\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Farts%2F20170519%2F141153%2F&h=f18d762e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/life/arts/20170519/141153/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T13:41:37.000Z","msg":"真係無睇過呢篇文"},{"pid":"361c28f3f6927999c6169e6161f74d63b8f08e28","tid":1130942,"uid":92377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2df8e42272b25c6f40ac7498eb80bbe72365459b","tid":1130942,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:13:38.000Z","msg":"我鐘意王菲多d, 王靖雯乜水黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#曲到圓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T13:43:28.000Z","msg":"無啦啦做乜要將王靖雯同佢比較<br />\n兩個唔同人 唔同歌路"},{"pid":"47ff3947c560d9051f82d8d3ece232c9bd782f2f","tid":113